Global Presence | SPX Corporation
















































home
our company
global presence










  GLOBAL PRESENCEWith a market presence in approximately 15 countries, SPX Corporation infrastructure products and services serve customers throughout the world, including:The Americas: Whether providing electrical transformers to improve system reliability or automate payment processing for mass transit systems in U.S. cities, SPX solutions help enhance everyday life.Europe, Middle East and Africa: SPX detection and measurement tools are utilized across Europe for underground utility protection, safety and security while our cooling towers help provide stable air conditioning to the stunning skyscrapers of the Middle East.Asia Pacific: SPX has a strong commitment to serving Asian markets, particularly in the fast-growing economies of China and India, where we provide state-of-the-art cooling systems and other thermal components.



